# The Vercel app lives only in landing-v2/. Ignore the heavy root-level Google
# Ads working files (images, PDFs, scripts) so the deploy upload stays small.
# Patterns are anchored with a leading slash = repo root ONLY, so nothing inside
# landing-v2/ is affected, and Vercel's default node_modules exclusion is kept.
/*.png
/*.jpeg
/*.jpg
/*.pdf
/*.csv
/*.py
/code
/landing
/Assets and Deliverables
/Presentations
/.next
/.tmp.driveupload
landing-v2/node_modules
landing-v2/.next
